General.Name: Tigers Realm Coal Ltd
General.Description: Tigers Realm Coal Limited engages in the identification, exploration, development, mining, and sale of coal from deposits in Russia and Asia. The company holds 100% interests in the Amaam North project; and 80% interests in the Amaam tenement located in the Bering Basin, Chukotka province. It also owns and operates the Beringovsky port and coal terminal located to the northeast of the Amaam North deposit. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Moscow, Russia.
